1
00:00:00,867 --> 00:00:02,068
I know.

2
00:00:03,236 --> 00:00:05,505
Don't miss me too much, okay?

3
00:00:06,406 --> 00:00:07,674
Don't worry.

4
00:00:09,609 --> 00:00:10,443
Okay.

5
00:00:12,412 --> 00:00:13,313
Love you.

6
00:00:14,314 --> 00:00:15,015
Bye.

7
00:00:25,925 --> 00:00:26,893
This feels like...

8
00:00:26,893 --> 00:00:28,228
a scene from a music video.

9
00:00:30,397 --> 00:00:31,965
Two people meeting by chance...

10
00:00:31,965 --> 00:00:33,166
after years of being apart.

11
00:00:38,104 --> 00:00:40,140
I heard your voice just now...

12
00:00:41,141 --> 00:00:42,308
and thought I was hearing things.

13
00:00:46,813 --> 00:00:48,181
I thought you'd settled abroad.

14
00:00:48,748 --> 00:00:50,383
What brings you back so suddenly?

15
00:00:52,585 --> 00:00:53,520
I'm back...

16
00:00:54,621 --> 00:00:55,822
...to see you.

17
00:00:59,926 --> 00:01:01,194
Quite the nostalgia trip.

18
00:01:02,829 --> 00:01:04,097
We haven't been in touch for years.

19
00:01:04,998 --> 00:01:06,800
I never expected to run into you here.

20
00:01:09,102 --> 00:01:10,036
I can't tell...

21
00:01:10,036 --> 00:01:11,471
if this is a surprise...

22
00:01:11,471 --> 00:01:12,572
or a total shock.

23
00:01:16,709 --> 00:01:17,977
It's not like I didn't try to reach out.

24
00:01:21,247 --> 00:01:22,549
Save the excuses.

25
00:01:23,383 --> 00:01:25,251
We were friends, after all.

26
00:01:25,251 --> 00:01:27,153
You didn't even tell me you got married.

27
00:01:27,153 --> 00:01:28,388
I'm not married.

28
00:01:31,458 --> 00:01:32,859
"Don't miss me too much"...

29
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:33,960
...and "Love you"?

30
00:01:36,529 --> 00:01:37,464
Chen Tian-you,

31
00:01:38,097 --> 00:01:38,965
I didn't think you'd still...

32
00:01:38,965 --> 00:01:40,633
talk to people like that.

33
00:01:42,669 --> 00:01:43,536
That was an old lady...

34
00:01:43,536 --> 00:01:45,071
who looked after me overseas.

35
00:01:45,338 --> 00:01:46,539
A local there.

36
00:01:46,539 --> 00:01:47,907
She was always on my case...

37
00:01:51,878 --> 00:01:53,146
about learning to say "I love you."

38
00:01:54,013 --> 00:01:54,881
That's nice.

39
00:01:58,051 --> 00:01:59,285
But what about you?

40
00:02:00,253 --> 00:02:01,354
Are you married?

41
00:02:01,354 --> 00:02:02,822
Has life been treating you well?

42
00:02:02,822 --> 00:02:03,857
Do you have kids?

43
00:02:06,025 --> 00:02:07,227
I'm not married either.

44
00:02:14,501 --> 00:02:15,368
Back then,

45
00:02:15,368 --> 00:02:16,636
you just up and left.

46
00:02:17,003 --> 00:02:18,438
You left me for someone else,

47
00:02:18,438 --> 00:02:19,639
and then went radio silent.

48
00:02:22,275 --> 00:02:23,376
So why didn't you marry him?

49
00:02:25,812 --> 00:02:27,180
He just wasn't the one.

50
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,181
We broke up a long time ago.

51
00:02:31,017 --> 00:02:32,018
I'm still waiting.

52
00:02:39,425 --> 00:02:40,693
Have you found him yet?

53
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:44,998
I have.

54
00:02:48,368 --> 00:02:50,336
Then don't keep him waiting too long.

55
00:02:50,937 --> 00:02:52,038
I've got a meeting to get to.

56
00:02:52,539 --> 00:02:53,540
Let's catch up soon.
